Happy Giving Tuesday🖤Help us continue bringing Dracula back bigger and better each year. I want to continue bringing performance opportunities to dancers in Los Angeles and to continue growing the company and bringing an outdated ballet culture into present times. I would love to add more shows, dancers, props, scenery, etc to this production. Link in my stories to donate 🖤 

We started from scratch in 2022 so the fact we have done it two years in a row is mind blowing to me!! So excited for next years shows. 

More info on donation page! Xoxox Robbie
